               stealing, on the <rs id="t18260622-57-cd273" type="crimeDate">17th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260622-57-off272 t18260622-57-cd273"></join>, 6 pairs of stockings, value 8s., 3d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18260622-57-victim439" type="victimName">
                  Robert 
                  Plant
               <interp inst="t18260622-57-victim439" type="surname" value="Plant"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260622-57-victim439" type="given" value="Robert"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260622-57-victim439" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260622-57-off272 t18260622-57-victim439"></join>
